{"title":"内建常用模块","slug":"2019-01-25-builtmodu","date":"2019-01-25T01:29:48.000Z","updated":"2019-01-25T05:16:18.745Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2019-01-25-builtmodu.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<h4 id=\"简单模块\"><a href=\"#简单模块\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"简单模块\"></a>简单模块</h4><ul>\n<li><p><code>decimal</code>提供高精度的数字，允许控制计算过程中的各个方面，包括数字的位数和四舍五入。要做到这些，需要创建一个本地的上下文环境然后修改其设定。例如</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> decimal <span class=\"keyword\">import</span> localcontext , Decimal</span><br><span class=\"line\">a = Decimal(<span class=\"string\">'1.3'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">b = Decimal(<span class=\"string\">'1.7'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">with</span> localcontext() <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> ctx:</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tctx.prec = <span class=\"number\">3</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tprint(a / b)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">0.765</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>NumPy</code>，任何涉及数组的计算密集型任务都应该使用它。<code>NumPy</code>提供了数组对象比列表有着更好的性能，更加适合数学运算。导入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> numpy <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> np</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>…</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>random</code>包含各种函数解决随机数和随机挑选问题。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>从序列中随机调出元素<code>random.choice(seq)</code></li>\n<li>从序列中随机取出N个元素，<code>random.sample(seq,n)</code></li>\n<li>将序列原地打乱<code>random.shuffle(seq)</code></li>\n<li><code>random.randint(a,b)</code>产生<code>[a,b]</code>之间的数字</li>\n<li><code>random.random()</code>产生0到1之间的均匀分布的浮点数</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>datetime</code>模块。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>其中的<code>timedelta</code>类代表一个时间间隔，创建一个实例，内部只存储<code>days</code>，<code>seconds</code>，<code>microseconds</code>，其他参数会自动转换。使用<code>c.days</code>查看内部的days，<code>c.seconds</code>查看内部的seconds，<code>c.total_seconds()</code>将内部三个参数全转化为秒为单位</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">timedelta([days[,seconds[,microseconds[,milliseconds[,minutes[,hours[,weeks]]]]]]])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><p><code>datetime</code>类代表特定的日期。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">datetime(year,month,day[,hour[,minute[,second[,microsecond[,tzinfo]]]]])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>当两个日期相减时返回一个<code>timedelta</code>对象。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"python","slug":"python","count":7,"path":"api/tags/python.json"}]}